data.description: Easy living in this sweet Hamilton Heights bungalow.  Comfortable & light filled traditional open plan w/front porch for relaxing & kibitzing w/the neighbors.  Bamboo floors in Main Living areas & Master Bedrm. New Carpet in Bedrms. New Interior Paint.  Landscaped w/Fruit Trees, Raised Planting Beds & some charming Exotic Plants - the property blooms all year! Fully fenced & private back yard.  Walk to Neighborhood Park & nearby City Trails. RV/Boat storage available. Minutes to Port Townsend!
